Ntombovuyo Silberose Nkopane bụ onye ndọrọ ndọrọ ọchịchị South Africa
Kemgbe afọ 2014, ọ bụ onye otu Eastern Cape Provincial Legislature, na-anọchite anya African National Congress
N'abalị iri na isii n'ọnwa Ọgọstụ afọ 2022, a họpụtara ya dị ka onye otu Executive Council (MEC) nke na-ahụ maka ọrụ ọha na eze na akụrụngwa.
Àtụ:Members of the Eastern Cape Provincial Legislature
